trans-unit.source: Contains the collection of controls that the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage" /> uses.
trans-unit.target: Contém a coleção de controles que o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage" /> usa.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage" /> that contains this collection of controls.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage" /> que contém essa coleção de controles.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.TabPageControlCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.TabPageControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds a control to the collection.
The specified control is added to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: O controle especificado é adicionado ao final da coleção.

trans-unit.source: If the control is already a child of another control, it is removed from the other control.
trans-unit.target: Se o controle já é filho de outro controle, ele é removido do outro controle.

trans-unit.source: The following code example creates a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> with one <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir cria um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> com um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage>.

trans-unit.source: This example uses the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.TabPageControlCollection.Add%2A> method to add a single control, `button1`, to the `tabPage1`.
trans-unit.target: Este exemplo usa o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.TabPageControlCollection.Add%2A> método para adicionar um controle único, `button1`, para o `tabPage1`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> property is used to get the `tabPage1` controls collection to add controls to the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> propriedade é usada para obter o `tabPage1` controles de coleção para adicionar controles à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Drawing> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms> namespaces for this example.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Drawing> e <xref:System.Windows.Forms> namespaces para este exemplo.

trans-unit.source: The specified control is a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage" />.
trans-unit.target: O controle especificado é um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage" />.
